headline: Revenue Estimates Dip, But Analysts Stay Bullish on Palo Alto Networks (PANW)
summary: Palo Alto Networks, Inc. (NASDAQ:PANW) is one of the 10 AI Stocks Investors are Watching. On June 26, Stifel analyst Adam Borg reiterated a “Buy” rating on the stock with a $225.00 price target.
